                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d1657e111">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        <i>Analysis</i>:
This acquisition is for end products for use in the United States
and is set aside for small business concerns. The Buy American statute
applies. Perform the steps in <xref href="25.502.dita#FAR_25_502"
                              base="i1091565"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly">25.502</xref>(a).
Offer C is evaluated as a foreign end product because it is the
product of a small business but is not a domestic end product (see <xref href="25.502.dita#FAR_25_502"
                              base="i1091565"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly">25.502</xref>(c)(4)). After applying
the 30 percent  factor,
the evaluated price of Offer C is $13,260. Award on
Offer B at $10,700 (see <xref href="25.502.dita#FAR_25_502"
